<h2>又有${blogs.size()}篇雄文来袭，欢迎大家点击围观，信息如下：</h2>
<br/>
<br/>
<table border="1">
    <thead>
    <tr>
        <th>标题</th>
        <th>网站</th>
        <th>作者</th>
        <th>分组</th>
    </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    #foreach($blog in $blogs)
    <tr>
        <td><a href="$blog.link">$blog.title</a></td>
        <td>$blog.website</td>
        <td>$blog.author.name</td>
        <td>$blog.author.groupName</td>
    </tr>
    #end
    </tbody>
</table>